<% offer_state =  if @booking_offer.accepted_at.present?
                    "accepted"
                  elsif @booking_offer.rejected_at.present?
                    "rejected"
                  end
%>
Hello <%= @booking_offer.booking.assignee.name %>!
Offer no. <%= @booking_offer.id %> of booking <%= @booking_offer.booking.id %> was <%= "#{offer_state}" %> by <%= "#{@booking_offer.booking.customer.first_name} #{@booking_offer.booking.customer.last_name}" %>.
Please check the booking (<%= booking_url(@booking_offer.booking, locale: I18n.locale) %>) state.
Have a great day!
